game.name: Shiba Rescue Dogs and Puppies
game.description:
Shiba is a very brave and smart dog with some cute and lovely puppies. Now it is a sleep time for all. But, unfortunately they all have forgot the way to their bed and still struggling to reach to their destination. Can you help them out? Join Shiba Rescue Dogs and Puppies and get ready to help their puppies to find out their bed. The best part is that you will be rewarded with the bonus points for your every successful effort. 

Hurry up! These puppies are very small to complete the task on their own. Shiba relies on your skills, so try to put your best to draw the path they need to follow on the floor you see on the screen in this brand new arcade game! You would also find out some big dogs on the path, so try to avoid them to clear a path for the puppies. It will be amazing to witness lots of new fun challenges in each level. Test your logic and reflexes to complete all the levels with the best score in this cute html5 puzzle challenge! 

When you click the play button, you would spot a big checkerboard with big dogs, beds and puppies. Place your own arrows in the checkerboard to guide your puppies toward their bed! The completion of each level will only be possible if each puppy will reach to their bed successfully. Give this arcade challenge a try to work your memory in this new arcade game! The cute graphics, easy controls and 40 engaging levels are perfect for kids and the young ones. Enjoy in more puzzle challenges on atmegame.com, no download required!
